title: Tin Foil Hat #48: The Rt 91 Vegas Swapcast with the Pirate Life Radio's Tait Fletcher
description: Welcome to another crazy episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli.  This episode Ryan and Sam do a swapcast with Pirate Life Radio's Tait Fletcher.  You have asked for a Tin Foil Hat about the Las Vegas Shooting and here it is.  We go deep Homeboy. Thank you for listening!
